## Backup Script

A Bash backup script was created to automatically back up the website files.

### Purpose

The script copies the website directory from `/var/www/html` to a backup folder located in the user's home directory.

### Benefits

* Protects website files from accidental deletion
* Allows quick restoration of the website
* Demonstrates Linux scripting skills

### Usage

```bash
./backup.sh
```

### Output

```text
Website backup completed successfully
```

The successful creation of the `website_backup` folder verifies that the script executed correctly.
